This place feels a bit suspicious, doesn't it?

Oh! You have quite the discerning eye to come to
my aid! I was about to be in a very dire
situation!

It seems like we already have some comrades!
Please take care of them!

I'm glad it seems like everyone is safe.

Thank you! You seem quite strong. Alright, since

the Village of Lewd Demons.
